<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0;">
  <div style="background-color: #1a1a2e; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="color: #e94560; margin: 0; font-size: 32px;">MUZAYEDE</h1>
    <p style="color: #eee; margin-top: 5px;">Turkiye'nin Online Muzayede Platformu</p>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background-color: #ffffff;">
    <h2 style="color: #1a1a2e;">Hosgeldiniz, {{firstName}}!</h2>

    <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">
      Muzayede platformumuza katildiginiz icin tesekkur ederiz. Binlerce eseri kesfedebilir,
      muzayedelere katilabilir ve koleksiyonunuzu buyutebilirsiniz.
    </p>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="color: #1a1a2e; margin-top: 0;">Ilk Adimlar:</h3>
      <ul style="color: #555; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Profilinizi tamamlayin</li>
        <li>Ilgi alanlarinizi secin</li>
        <li>Canli muzayedeleri kesfet</li>
        <li>Ilk teklifinizi verin</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #e94560; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;">
      Platformu Kesfet
    </a>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999; background-color: #f0f0f0;">
    <p>Bu e-posta Muzayede platformuna kayit oldugunuz icin gonderilmistir.</p>
    <p>Muzayede Platform &copy; 2026 - Tum haklari saklidir.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
